<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id060513bd-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007"><num value="3007">§ 3007.</num><heading> Publication of Harmonized Tariff Schedule</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id060513be-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall compile and publish, at appropriate intervals, and keep up to date the Harmonized Tariff Schedule and related information in the form of printed copy; and, if, in its judgment, such format would serve the public interest and convenience—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id060513bf-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> in the form of microfilm images; or</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id060513c0-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> in the form of electronic media.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id060513c1-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Content</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Publications under subsection (a), in whatever format, shall contain—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id060513c2-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/b/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> the then current Harmonized Tariff Schedule;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id060513c3-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/b/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> statistical annotations and related statistical information formulated under <ref href="/us/usc/t19/s1484/f">section 1484(f) of this title</ref>; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id060513c4-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s3007/b/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> such other matters as the Commission considers to be necessary or appropriate to carry out the purposes enumerated in the Preamble to the Convention.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id060513c5-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/418/tI/s1207">Pub. L. 100–418, title I, § 1207</ref>, <date date="1988-08-23">Aug. 23, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/1151">102 Stat. 1151</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/104/295/s21/e/10">Pub. L. 104–295, § 21(e)(10)</ref>, <date date="1996-10-11">Oct. 11, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/3531">110 Stat. 3531</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id060513c6-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id060513c7-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="id060513c8-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The Harmonized Tariff Schedule, referred to in subsecs. (a) and (b)(1), is not set out in the Code. See Publication of Harmonized Tariff Schedule note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t19/s1202">section 1202 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id060513c9-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—Subsec. (b)(2). <ref href="/us/pl/104/295">Pub. L. 104–295</ref> substituted “1484(f)” for “1484(e)”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
